Wesley Sneijder has apologised after unwittingly launching his knife range in Galatasaray colours on the 15th anniversary of two Leeds United supporters being stabbed to death in Istanbul .
Leeds fans , Kevin Speight and Christopher Loftus were killed before the UEFA Cup semi-final-final first leg against Istanbul on April 5 , 2000 .
A minute 's silence will be held before Leeds and Blackburn Rovers meet at Elland Road on Saturday .